title: Fortinet FortiMail Mail Queue Info
agents: snmp
catalog: hw/network/fortinet
license: GPL
distribution: check_mk
description:
 This Check will display every exisiting Queue on a Fortinet Mail Server and the amount and
 size of the queued mails within those.
 The Check can go into warning or ciritical if the amount of mails in the Queue is too high.
 The default thresholds are:
 100 Mails for warning and 200 Mails for ciritical.

discovery:
 One check per Mail Queue will be created.
